Class ExecuteServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team.web.service.impl.ExecuteServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExecuteService

    @Service
public class ExecuteServiceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExecuteService
    A Service which serves for handling Order executions performances to the database (Which on this project, stored in Engine.getAfterExecutionOrderAndTransactionDTO()).

    This service is ready for future use of database implementations.
